sary services/ports/software removed", "USB/removable media restricted"], "cross_check_validation": [], "authenticity_check": "Is evidence authentic (not paper compliance)?", "dispute_action": "Raise formal comment if L2 Sufficient rating is disputed", "rating_options": ["Compliant", "Partially Compliant", "Non-Compliant", "N/A"], "rating": null}'::jsonb);
